xwikidoc.content:
== Description ==

Creates various types of charts using [[Chart.js>>http://www.chartjs.org/]].

=== Usage ===

{{code language="none"}}
{{chartjs type="..." options="{...}"}}
{
  "labels": [...],
  "datasets": [...]
}
{{/chartjs}}
{{/code}}

=== Parameters ===

